channel.description:
[center][b]This is the code you need to make you go down with a ladder[/b][/center]

[i]if ((objectID == Object ID) && (objectX == Object X coord) && (objectY == Object Y coord)) {
	toX = Your X coord;
	toY = Your Y coord;
	heightLevel = 0; // Ladder Down
	setAnimation(828);
	break;
	}[/i]

[center][b]This is the code you need to make you go up with a ladder[/b][/center]

[i]if ((objectID == Object ID) && (objectX == Object X coord) && (objectY == Object Y coord)) {
	toX = Your X coord;
	toY = Your Y coord;
	heightLevel = 1; // Ladder Up
	setAnimation(828);
	break;
	}[/i]

[b]You can also let you go higher or go underground... Just change the 'heightLevel' to the height you want.[/b]

[center][size=16pt]BE SURE YOU PLACE IT AT THE RIGHT PLACE IN 'client.java'!!![/size][/center]
